{"tid":613584,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"名校secrets 知衰認錯","createTime":"2018-04-01T18:43:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-01T19:59:11.000Z","uid":174155,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d6ea28fdb9670b39941b7d46a8e6c18e9f7c6c25","tid":613584,"uid":174155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T18:43:58.000Z","msg":"凌晨先出post唔知大家收唔收貨呢？<br />\n《道歉聲明》<br />\n<br />\n名校Secrets團隊現向各位關注「文章標題修改及ADMIN態度惡劣」一事的各位讀者表示歉意。特別是受影響的吳同學，請接受我們摯誠的道歉﹗<br />\n<br />\n涉事之admin已被永久終止職務。事件之中，我們深刻反省到：<br />\n<br />\n（1） 該admin對投稿者態度惡劣，是錯誤的示範；<br />\n（2） 改動原圖及下標題時產生誤導，偏離po主原意，是為失職。<br />\n<br />\n為此，名校Secrets全體仝人再次向各位深深致歉。經過今次教訓，我們承諾會積極檢討審批流程及機制，今後讀者來圖修改後必須經得同意，方會發帖；並將於本月15日公開發佈明確的版規，現誠邀各位參與提供寶貴意見，還望各位不吝指導。<br />\n<br />\n意見收集form：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/WBYpTclYkrHL9mTC3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2FWBYpTclYkrHL9mTC3&d=ydmL7MEAMtVscdTyxdshVQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=bc631e59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/WBYpTclYkrHL9mTC3</a><br />\n<br />\n感謝各位。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/024346_3b667bab62b9780c1d7b942b07f7f152.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F024346_3b667bab62b9780c1d7b942b07f7f152.png&h=48660747&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"259b5e06efeaa5d90d5800dd4310b32165edd5e9","tid":613584,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T18:46:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81cb551aeacdff30c9212c21f9628cb603962518","tid":613584,"uid":137766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T18:49:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img